..#L274-L299\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L300-L343\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L344-L387\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L388-L398\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L409-L410\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L111-L163\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L164-L211\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L212-L264\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L265-L273\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L274-L299\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L300-L343\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L344-L387\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L388-L398\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/13.1.0-next.0/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L409-L410\n-->"
}